{
  "stem": "8753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I finished seventh grades, elementary school, which was equal to junior high school, I believe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then when the Russians occupied our village, the-- many children went to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they were already 14, 13, 14.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the Russians want to organize a sixth grade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there weren't enough children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the teacher came to ask my parents to ask me, would I come back to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wasn't happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like going backwards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they explained that they teach more, which they did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They taught in the sixth grade more than the Polish school in the seventh grade.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember they-- we had algebra, which I never had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I enjoyed algebra very much, which we never had in the Polish seventh grade.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had some Ukrainian lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I think twice a week, we had Ukrainian lessons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the same school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the population was about half Polish and half Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got along.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was quite-- in fact, we, the Jewish people, got along with the non-Jewish people, most of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we heard some anti-Semitic remarks here and there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But not-- I remember when I was quite little, my mother wouldn't allow me to play with the non-Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, they used coarse language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was shielding me from the anti-Semitic remarks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I just had a neighbor, a little girl that I used to play with as a little girl.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- I mean, that neighbor my mother OKed for me to play with her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when I came to school, I-- that's the contact I had with the Polish and Ukrainian children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember in the fourth and fifth grade, I befriended a girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her father was an engineer.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
